sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant A as iOS App
  participant Apple as Apple ID
  participant Auth as Firebase Auth
  participant Local as SwiftData
  participant FS as Firestore
  U->>A: Choose Sign in with Apple
  A->>Apple: Authorization request + nonce
  Apple-->>A: Identity token
  A->>Auth: OAuth credential
  Auth-->>A: Firebase UID/session
  A->>Local: Resolve user-scoped local state
  A->>FS: Create/merge user profile
  FS-->>A: Profile state or rule error
